{
  "text": "where M is anR 2 index, and \u03b7 MN M is an invariant tensor(an \"eta-symbol\" in the language of [CITATION_1] ), which is basically just the projector of a pair of symmetric R 1 indices into R 2 . Invariance of this tensor",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "119091265"
